{
  "description": "A stunning, wide-angle view of a vibrant sunset over a thick layer of fog. The sun, a brilliant orange sphere, is positioned just above the horizon, partially obscured by the fog. Below the sun, the fog appears as a sea of white and gray, creating a dramatic contrast with the warm hues of the sky. The faint silhouette of a bridge can be seen rising from the fog, adding a sense of scale and depth. The sky transitions from a deep orange near the horizon to a lighter, golden yellow higher up. The overall effect is one of peacefulness and breathtaking natural beauty.",
